<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>관리자가 예약을 생성했습니다</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 24px; background: #f5f6f8; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; color: #1f2933;"
  >
    <table
      role="presentation"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      width="100%"
      style="max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e4e7eb;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 32px 32px 16px 32px;">
          <h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #102a43;">
            새 예약이 등록되었습니다
          </h1>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
            안녕하세요{{#if name}} <strong>{{name}}</strong>님{{/if}},
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
            관리자가 회원님 명의로 회의실 예약을 생성했습니다.
            {{#if adminName}}(처리자: <strong>{{adminName}}</strong>){{/if}}
          </p>

          <table
            role="presentation"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            width="100%"
            style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; border-collapse: collapse; background: #f0f4f8; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;"
          >
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #52606d; width: 88px;">제목</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #102a43; font-weight: 600;">{{title}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #52606d; border-top: 1px solid #d9e2ec;">회의실</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #102a43; border-top: 1px solid #d9e2ec;">{{roomName}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #52606d; border-top: 1px solid #d9e2ec;">시간</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #102a43; border-top: 1px solid #d9e2ec;">{{startAt}} ~ {{endAt}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #52606d; border-top: 1px solid #d9e2ec;">예약 ID</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 12px; color: #102a43; border-top: 1px solid #d9e2ec; font-family: 'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, monospace;">{{bookingId}}</td>
            </tr>
          </table>

          {{#if dashboardUrl}}
            <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; text-align: center;">
              <a
                href="{{dashboardUrl}}"
                style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;"
              >캘린더에서 확인</a>
            </p>
          {{/if}}

          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #52606d;">
            본인이 인지하지 못한 예약이라면 관리자에게 즉시 확인 부탁드립니다.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td
          style="padding: 16px 32px; background: #fafbfc; border-top: 1px solid #e4e7eb; font-size: 12px; color: #829ab1;"
        >
          © {{appName}}
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
